title: The Nerves - One Way Ticket (2008)
description:
The Nerves
One Way Ticket
Released Nov. 11, 2008

The long awaited album of Nerves singles and hits.  The band featured guitarist Jack Lee, bassist Peter Case, and drummer Paul Collins. All three members composed songs and sang. They lasted just a short time and self-released only one self-titled four-song EP in 1976, featuring the songs "Hanging on the Telephone" (Lee), "When You Find Out" (Case), "Give Me Some Time" (Lee), and "Working Too Hard" (Collins). For fans of late 70&#039;s early 80&#039;s power pop, the Plimsouls, or The Beat (Paul Collins Beat), this is a must-have.

This is a 320kbps MP3 rip, VBR.  Very high quality.  I downloaded from iTunes and then converted to MP3s from that source.
